data.description: Welcome to this STUNNING 4-bedroom 3 bath home located in the highly sought after neighborhood of Laurel Lakes! When you enter this beautiful home, you will be blown away by its breathtaking views of the serene lake! The tray ceilings make this home feel so grand and the gourmet kitchen features solid wood cabinetry, providing ample storage space, a breakfast bar and is equipped with all stainless-steel appliances. The master bedroom is huge and has wood laminate floors throughout that add a touch of elegance to the space and has a his & her double vanity sinks! Step outside onto the screened porch with that gorgeous lake view and then take a dip in the heated spa as you soak in the beauty of your surroundings. This gated community offers a multitude of amenities, from the pool to a modern fitness center, a club house and tennis court. Located near Top A+ rated schools, the Gulf beaches and shopping centers don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours. Schedule a showing today!!!
